GLOIN: I've got parasites as big as my arm!

881
01:06:52,888 --> 01:06:55,823
我的是最大的，我有巨型寄生虫！
KILI: Mine are the biggest parasites, I've got huge parasites!

882
01:06:57,433 --> 01:06:58,151
我们全身都是！
NORI: We're riddled!

883
01:06:58,166 --> 01:06:59,014
对，我全身都是！
ORI: Yes, I'm riddled!

884
01:06:59,015 --> 01:07:00,312
对，我们很糟
DORI: Yes we are, badly!

885
01:07:00,429 --> 01:07:03,239
你要我们怎么办？
WILLIAM: What would you have us do then?

886
01:07:03,528 --> 01:07:05,114
放他们走？
Let 'em all go?

887
01:07:06,427 --> 01:07:09,026
你以为我不知道你在干嘛？
Well...

888
01:07:06,427 --> 01:07:09,026
WILLIAM: You think I don't know what you're up to.

889
01:07:09,136 --> 01:07:13,643
这个小狐狸把我们当成傻子！
This little ferret... is taking us for fools!

890
01:07:13,720 --> 01:07:14,486
狐狸？
BILBO: Ferret? .

891
01:07:14,487 --> 01:07:15,444
傻子？
BILBO: Ferret? C BERT: Fools?

892
01:07:15,483 --> 01:07:18,061
黎明将把你们全带走！
GANDALF: The dawn will take you all!

893
01:07:19,832 --> 01:07:21,527
- 那是谁？ - 不知道
C WILLIAM: Who's that? C BERT: No idea.

894
01:07:21,645 --> 01:07:23,246
能把他也吃了吗？
TOM: Can we eat him too?

895
01:07:26,478 --> 01:07:29,593
[Trolls scream as they change to stone]

896
01:07:41,827 --> 01:07:45,771
[All dwarves laugh of joy]

897
01:07:48,642 --> 01:07:51,085
把你的脚从我背上拿开
DWALIN: Ooh, get your foot out of my back!

898
01:08:00,986 --> 01:08:03,007
我能问问你去哪了吗？
THORIN: Where did you go to, if I may ask?

899
01:08:03,327 --> 01:08:04,447
往前看
GANDALF: To look ahead.

900
01:08:05,070 --> 01:08:06,296
什么把你带回来的？
THORIN: What brought you back?

901
01:08:06,389 --> 01:08:08,011
往后看
GANDALF: Looking behind.

902
01:08:09,113 --> 01:08:10,394
糟糕的事
Nasty business.

903
01:08:10,614 --> 01:08:12,150
幸好他们都没事
Still they all are in one piece.

904
01:08:12,221 --> 01:08:13,757
该谢谢你的小偷
No thanks to your burglar.

905
01:08:15,242 --> 01:08:17,872
他懂得拖延时间
He had the nose to play for time.

906
01:08:18,383 --> 01:08:20,483
你们没人想到这点
None of the rest of you thought of that.

907
01:08:23,100 --> 01:08:26,152
他们肯定是从伊顿荒原过来的
GANDALF: They must have come down from the Ettenmoors.

908
01:08:26,199 --> 01:08:28,813
从何时起这些山怪会往南走这么远？
THORIN: Since when the mountain trolls venture this far South?

909
01:08:29,134 --> 01:08:30,905
没多久
GANDALF: Oh, not for an age...

910
01:08:32,017 --> 01:08:35,217
只是在黑暗势力统治这领土后
Not since a darker power ruled these lands.

911
01:08:41,562 --> 01:08:44,306
他们不能在白天行动
They could not have moved in daylight.

912
01:08:45,351 --> 01:08:47,486
这附近肯定有洞穴
THORIN: There must be a cave nearby.

913
01:08:58,407 --> 01:09:00,662
真是臭
OFUR: Oh what's that stench?!

914
01:09:00,897 --> 01:09:03,568
这是巨怪囤物洞
GANDALF: It's a troll hoard.

915
01:09:04,342 --> 01:09:06,418
别随意摸
Be careful what you touch.

916
01:09:06,879 --> 01:09:11,072
[All dwarves cough from the smell]

917
01:09:19,543 --> 01:09:22,924
让这些就这么丢着似乎很可耻
BOFUR: Seems a shame just to leave it lying around.

918
01:09:23,908 --> 01:09:25,296
谁都可以来拿
Anyone could take it.

919
01:09:25,492 --> 01:09:26,612
同意
GLOIN: Agreed.

920
01:09:26,750 --> 01:09:28,218
诺力
Nori, come here.

921
01:09:28,453 --> 01:09:29,853
拿个铲子来
Get a shovel.

922
01:09:47,245 --> 01:09:50,045
这些剑不是巨怪造的
THORIN: These swords were not made by any troll.

923
01:09:55,230 --> 01:09:58,668
也不是人类铁匠造的
GANDALF: Nor were they made by any smith among men.

924
01:10:04,120 --> 01:10:06,211
它们是在贡多林锻造的
These were forged in Gondolin...

925
01:10:06,610 --> 01:10:09,133
由第一纪元的高等精灵铸造
by the High Elves, of the First Age.

926
01:10:10,569 --> 01:10:13,176
没有比这更精良的刀刃
You could not wish for a finer blade.

927
01:10:24,542 --> 01:10:26,211
奇力，好了
GLOIN: Kíli, come, come.

928
01:10:29,532 --> 01:10:30,932
好，快点
NORI: Alright, come.

929
01:10:39,135 --> 01:10:42,001
我们在做长远储备
GLOIN: We're making a long-term deposit.

930
01:10:42,900 --> 01:10:44,523
我们离开这个臭地方吧
THORIN: Let's get out of this foul place.

931
01:10:44,719 --> 01:10:45,839
快点，走
Come on, let's go.

932
01:10:46,453 --> 01:10:48,380
波弗，葛罗林，诺力.
Bofur, Glóin, Nori.

933
01:11:07,962 --> 01:11:09,329
比尔博
C GANDALF: Bilbo. C Hm?

934
01:11:11,389 --> 01:11:14,342
拿着，这配你差不多
Here. This is about your size.

935
01:11:20,509 --> 01:11:21,884
我不能拿
I can't take this.

936
01:11:22,462 --> 01:11:25,709
这是精灵造的刀刃，意味着
The blade is of Elvish make, which means

937
01:11:25,833 --> 01:11:30,252
半兽人或妖精靠近时会发出蓝光
it will glow blue when orcs or goblins are nearby.

938
01:11:30,800 --> 01:11:33,118
我……我，从没用过剑
I-  I have never used a sword in my life.

939
01:11:33,391 --> 01:11:35,491
我也希望你永远不用剑
And I hope you'll never have to.

940
01:11:36,203 --> 01:11:38,333
但如果用上，记住
But if you do, remember this:

941
01:11:39,147 --> 01:11:44,419
真正的勇气……不是知道何时去杀人
True courage... is about knowing not when to take a life...

942
01:11:45,028 --> 01:11:47,270
而是何时去饶恕他人
but when to spare one.

943
01:11:52,671 --> 01:11:54,202
有东西来了！
DWALIN: Something's coming!

944
01:11:54,341 --> 01:11:55,207
甘道夫
BILBO: Gandalf!

945
01:11:55,286 --> 01:11:56,746
呆在一起
GANDALF: Stay together.

946
01:11:57,372 --> 01:11:58,898
快点！
Hurry, they're armed!

947
01:11:59,320 --> 01:12:01,079
备上武器
Arm yourselves!

948
01:12:18,133 --> 01:12:21,429
小偷！火！谋杀！
RADAGAST: Thieves! Fire! Murder!

949
01:12:23,459 --> 01:12:25,269
瑞达加斯特
GANDALF: Radagast.

950
01:12:26,175 --> 01:12:29,344
褐袍巫师瑞达加斯特
It's Radagast the Brown!

951
01:12:32,141 --> 01:12:33,881
你到底在做什么？
GANDALF: What on earth are you doing here?

952
01:12:33,917 --> 01:12:35,493
我在找你，甘道夫
I was looking for you, Gandalf.

953
01:12:35,595 --> 01:12:39,350
出事了，出大事了！
Something's wrong. Something's terribly wrong!

954
01:12:39,447 --> 01:12:40,567
什么事？
Yes?

955
01:12:46,161 --> 01:12:47,817
给我一分钟
RADAGAST: Just give me a minute, hm...

956
01:12:48,159 --> 01:12:49,279
不
No...

957
01:12:49,315 --> 01:12:51,399
有个想法，可是忘了，是……
I had a thought and, now I've lost it, it was-

958
01:12:51,400 --> 01:12:54,350
就在那儿，在舌尖！
it was was right there, on the tip of my tongue!

959
01:12:55,696 --> 01:12:58,373
噢，根本不是个想法！
Oh! It's not a thought at all!

960
01:12:58,889 --> 01:13:00,709
只是个……
It's just only a...

961
01:13:01,746 --> 01:13:02,964
竹节虫
stick insect.

962
01:13:07,236 --> 01:13:10,186
绿林病了，甘道夫
RADAGAST: The Greenwood is sick, Gandalf.

963
01:13:11,781 --> 01:13:15,591
黑暗降临了，万物不再生长了
A darkness has fallen over it, nothing glows anymore.

964
01:13:16,459 --> 01:13:18,120
至少好东西不再生长了
At least nothing good.

965
01:13:18,605 --> 01:13:21,105
空气满是腐烂臭味
The air is foul of decay,

966
01:13:21,683 --> 01:13:23,344
更糟的是网
but worse are the webs.

967
01:13:23,478 --> 01:13:25,319
网？什么意思？
GANDALF: Webs? What do you mean?

968
01:13:25,677 --> 01:13:29,604
蜘蛛，甘道夫，大蜘蛛
RADAGAST: Spiders, Gandalf. Giant ones.

969
01:13:29,799 --> 01:13:33,874
像是……安格利昂的卵 不然我就不是巫师（安格利昂：远古巨蜘蛛）
Some kind of spawn of... Ungoliant, or I'm not a wizard.

970
01:13:34,473 --> 01:13:36,377
我跟踪它们
I followed their trail.

971
01:13:36,746 --> 01:13:39,353
它们来自多尔哥多
They came from... Dol Guldur.

972
01:13:42,269 --> 01:13:43,669
多尔哥多？
GANDALF: Dol Guldur?

973
01:13:44,613 --> 01:13:47,525
但古堡荒废了
But the old fortress is abandoned.

974
01:13:48,510 --> 01:13:49,910
不，甘道夫
No, Gandalf.

975
01:13:51,659 --> 01:13:53,234
没有
It is not.

976
01:14:01,727 --> 01:14:04,874
那儿住着黑暗势力
RADAGAST (CONT'D): A dark power dwells in there...

977
01:14:05,117 --> 01:14:08,669
我从没遇到过的恶势力
such as I have never felt before.

978
01:14:10,191 --> 01:14:14,324
那是远古光环的影子
It is the shadow of an ancient aura.

979
01:14:20,505 --> 01:14:26,151
能够唤起亡灵的影子
One that can summon the spirits of the dead.

980
01:14:42,982 --> 01:14:44,933
我看见他了，甘道夫
I saw him, Gandalf.

981
01:14:45,598 --> 01:14:47,838
在黑暗里
From out of the darkness...

982
01:14:48,384 --> 01:14:52,327
死灵法师来了
the Necromancer has come!

983
01:15:19,947 --> 01:15:21,067
抱歉
Sorry.

984
01:15:21,483 --> 01:15:23,405
来点老托比
GANDALF: Try a little old Toby.

985
01:15:24,077 --> 01:15:25,481
能帮你冷静冷静
It'll help setting your nerves.

986
01:15:29,224 --> 01:15:30,706
再吐出来
Then out.

987
01:15:37,979 --> 01:15:40,469
死灵法师
Now... the Necromancer.

988
01:15:40,812 --> 01:15:42,212
你确定？
Are you sure?

989
01:15:55,881 --> 01:15:59,769
那不是来自……
RADAGAST: That is not... from the world...

990
01:15:59,965 --> 01:16:02,371
活人世界的
of the living.

991
01:16:03,470 --> 01:16:05,111
[Howlings]

992
01:16:07,772 --> 01:16:10,233
是狼吗？有……那儿有狼吗？
Was that a wolf? Are there- are there wolves out there?

993
01:16:10,499 --> 01:16:11,619
狼？
Wolves?

994
01:16:11,747 --> 01:16:13,567
不，那不是狼
No, that is not a wolf.

995
01:16:13,735 --> 01:16:15,842
[Growls]

996
01:16:27,729 --> 01:16:29,129
座狼探兵！
THORIN: Warg scouts!

997
01:16:29,448 --> 01:16:31,471
意味着半兽人群不远了
Which means an orc pack is not far behind.

998
01:16:31,494 --> 01:16:32,494
半兽人群？
Orc pack?

999
01:16:32,518 --> 01:16:35,605
除了家族外，你还和谁说了探险的事？
Who did you tell about your quest, beyond your kin?

1000
01:16:35,856 --> 01:16:36,666
没人
No one.

1001
01:16:36,689 --> 01:16:37,637
你和谁说了？
Who did you tell?

1002
01:16:37,692 --> 01:16:39,410
没人，我发誓！
No one, I swear!

1003
01:16:39,862 --> 01:16:41,416
都林血脉怎么了？
What in Dorin's name is going on?

1004
01:16:41,565 --> 01:16:43,385
你被追捕了
You're being hunted.

1005
01:16:44,172 --> 01:16:45,594
我们得离开这里
DWALIN: We have to get out of here.

1006
01:16:45,696 --> 01:16:49,592
不行，我们没有马，它们脱缰了
ORI: We can't! We have no ponies. They bolted.

1007
01:16:49,936 --> 01:16:51,342
我把它们引开
RADAGAST: I'll draw them off.

1008
01:16:51,526 --> 01:16:54,548
这些是刚达巴座狼，它们会追上你的
GANDALF: These are Gundabad wargs. They will outrun you!

1009
01:16:54,587 --> 01:16:57,608
这些是拉斯戈柏尔兔子
These are Rhosgobel rabbits.

1010
01:16:57,987 --> 01:17:00,420
我倒想让它们试试
I'd like to see them try.

1011
01:17:01,516 --> 01:17:04,710
[Wargs howl]

1012
01:17:12,320 --> 01:17:14,513
来抓我呀！
Come and get me!

1013
01:17:17,060 --> 01:17:18,880
[Radagast laughing]

1014
01:17:18,951 --> 01:17:21,309
[Wargs bark]

1015
01:17:24,004 --> 01:17:25,404
快点
GANDALF: Come on!

1016
01:17:53,683 --> 01:17:55,805
靠紧，前进！
Stay together. Move!

1017
01:18:06,930 --> 01:18:08,279
欧力，不！
THORIN: Ori, no!

1018
01:18:08,372 --> 01:18:09,888
回来
Come back.

1019
01:18:12,638 --> 01:18:14,738
你们全都跟上，跟上，快！
All of you, come on, come on! Quick!

1020
01:18:17,223 --> 01:18:19,541
你把我们带到哪去？
THORIN: Where're you leading us?

1021
01:19:16,041 --> 01:19:18,541
矮人渣在那边！

1022
01:19:20,541 --> 01:19:22,241
追！

1023
01:19:27,715 --> 01:19:28,566
前进！
GANDALF: Move!

1024
01:19:28,806 --> 01:19:30,283
跑
Run!

1025
01:19:47,067 --> 01:19:48,457
他们在那！
GLOIN: There they are!

1026
01:19:50,462 --> 01:19:52,673
这边！快点！
GANDALF: This way! Quickly!

1027
01:20:03,837 --> 01:20:05,618
我想还有很多要来！
KILI: I think there's more coming!

1028
01:20:06,626 --> 01:20:08,905
奇力，射死他们！
THORIN: Kíli! Shoot them!

1029
01:20:13,230 --> 01:20:14,619
我们被包围了！
FILI: We're surrounded!

1030
01:20:19,150 --> 01:20:20,889
甘道夫呢？
FILI: Where's Gandalf?

1031
01:20:20,983 --> 01:20:22,803
他抛弃我们了
DWALIN: He's abandoned us!

1032
01:20:29,249 --> 01:20:31,069
稳住阵地！
THORIN: Hold your ground!

1033
01:20:40,702 --> 01:20:42,363
这边，蠢货！
GANDALF: This way, you fools!

1034
01:20:42,997 --> 01:20:44,397
快，前进！
THORIN: Com'on, move!

1035
01:20:46,581 --> 01:20:48,401
快点，都快点！
Quickly! All of you!

1036
01:20:50,739 --> 01:20:52,139
快，快，快
THORIN: Go, go, go!

1037
01:21:02,609 --> 01:21:03,729
九，十
GANDALF: .. nine, ten...

1038
01:21:05,935 --> 01:21:08,448
奇力，跑
Kíli! Run!

1039
01:21:17,320 --> 01:21:20,374
[Hunting horn]

1040
01:21:23,025 --> 01:21:25,579
[Noise of arrows]

1041
01:21:48,078 --> 01:21:49,583
是精灵
Elves.

1042
01:21:52,407 --> 01:21:54,654
我看不清这通道通向哪儿
DWALIN: I cannot see where the pathway leads.

1043
01:21:54,746 --> 01:21:56,090
我们走还是不走？
Do we follow it or no?

1044
01:21:56,091 --> 01:21:57,545
当然要走了
BOFUR: We follow it, of course!

1045
01:22:01,568 --> 01:22:03,388
我认为那很明智
GANDALF: I think that would be wise.

1046
01:23:01,259 --> 01:23:03,819
伊姆拉里斯河谷
The valley of Imladris.

1047
01:23:05,287 --> 01:23:08,280
通常是叫另一个名字
In the common tongue, it's known by another name.

1048
01:23:09,504 --> 01:23:10,954
瑞文戴尔
Rivendell.

1049
01:23:13,652 --> 01:23:17,751
这里有大海东岸所剩无几的舒适小屋
GANDALF: Here lies the last homely house, east of the sea.

1050
01:23:20,048 --> 01:23:21,850
这就是你一直盘算的计划
This was your plan all along...

1051
01:23:22,561 --> 01:23:24,661
向敌人寻求庇护
to seek refuge with our enemy.

1052
01:23:25,179 --> 01:23:28,473
这里没有敌人，索林・橡木盾
You have no enemies here, Thorin Oakenshield.

1053
01:23:28,794 --> 01:23:33,190
这个河谷能找到的唯一敌意 就是你自己带来的这个
The only ill-will to be found in this valley is that which you bring yourself.

1054
01:23:33,722 --> 01:23:37,751
你认为精灵会为我们的探险赐福？
THORIN: You think the Elves... will give our quest their blessing?

1055
01:23:38,126 --> 01:23:39,649
他们会试图阻止我们的
They will try to stop us.

1056
01:23:39,876 --> 01:23:41,456
当然，他们会
Of course, they will.

1057
01:23:41,518 --> 01:23:43,970
但我们有问题需要解答
But we have questions that need to be answered.

1058
01:23:47,509 --> 01:23:51,009
如果我们想成功，就需要策略
If we are to be successful, this will need to be handled with tact...

1059
01:23:51,233 --> 01:23:52,633
尊重
and respect...

1060
01:23:52,804 --> 01:23:54,904
和不小的魅力
and no small degree of charm.

1061
01:23:55,677 --> 01:23:58,477
所以你要把沟通留给我来做
Which is why you will leave the talking to me.

1062
01:24:55,958 --> 01:24:57,358
米斯兰达（甘道夫的精灵名）
LINDIR: Mithrandir.

1063
01:24:58,364 --> 01:25:00,682
林德
Ah, Lindir.

1064
01:25:01,424 --> 01:25:02,824
提防着点
Stay sharp.

1065
01:25:03,824 --> 01:25:05,824
我听说你来河谷了

1066
01:25:06,376 --> 01:25:08,241
我有话和艾隆大人说
I must speak with Lord Elrond.

1067
01:25:08,335 --> 01:25:10,435
艾隆大人不在这里
My Lord Elrond is not here.

1068
01:25:10,600 --> 01:25:12,000
不在这里？
Not here?

1069
01:25:13,293 --> 01:25:14,693
他在哪儿？
Where is he?

1070
01:25:14,990 --> 01:25:18,855
[Hunting horn]

1071
01:25:27,059 --> 01:25:28,879
[Thorin speaks dwelvish]

1072
01:25:28,918 --> 01:25:30,872
靠拢！
Close ranks!

1073
01:25:54,947 --> 01:25:56,025
甘道夫！
Gandalf!

1074
01:25:56,220 --> 01:25:57,620
艾隆大人
Lоrd Εlrоn.

1075
01:25:59,620 --> 01:26:01,020
我的好朋友

1076
01:26:01,620 --> 01:26:02,820
你去哪了？

1077
01:26:03,420 --> 01:26:05,820
我们猎杀了一群来自南方的半兽人

1078
01:26:08,920 --> 01:26:11,120
在秘密隘口附近也杀了一些

1079
01:26:15,031 --> 01:26:18,468
半兽人离我们的边界这么近真是奇怪
Strange for orcs to come so close to our borders.

1080
01:26:19,352 --> 01:26:22,739
某个东西或某个人把他们引来了
Something or someone has drawn them near.

1081
01:26:22,809 --> 01:26:24,909
或许是因为我们
GANDALF: Ah, that may have been us.

1082
01:26:30,716 --> 01:26:33,448
欢迎索林，索恩之子
Welcome Thorin, son of Thráin.

1083
01:26:34,269 --> 01:26:36,369
我不认为我们见过面
I do not believe we have met.

1084
01:26:37,321 --> 01:26:39,217
你有你祖父的仪态
You have your Grandfather's bearing.

1085
01:26:40,554 --> 01:26:42,960
我认识索尔，在他统治山下时
I knew Thrór when he ruled under the mountain.

1086
01:26:43,046 --> 01:26:45,739
真的？他从没提到你
Indeed? He made no mention of you.

1087
01:26:50,100 --> 01:26:56,261
（精灵语）
[Speaks Elvish]

1088
01:26:57,415 --> 01:27:01,975
他在说什么？是在侮辱我们吗？
GLOIN: What is he saying? Does he offer us insult?

1089
01:27:02,171 --> 01:27:06,145
不，葛罗林大人，他在说给你们食物
No Master Glóin, he's offering you food.

1090
01:27:12,922 --> 01:27:14,042
Ah Well...

1091
01:27:14,435 --> 01:27:16,255
这样的话，带路吧
In that case, lead on.

1092
01:27:18,943 --> 01:27:21,823
试试看，就一口
Try it. Just a mouthful.

1093
01:27:22,027 --> 01:27:23,847
我不喜欢绿色食物
I don't like green food.

1094
01:27:24,808 --> 01:27:26,628
肉在哪？
Where's the meat?

1095
01:27:27,075 --> 01:27:29,307
他们有炸土豆吗？
Have they got any chips?

1096
01:27:30,097 --> 01:27:33,946
感谢你善意地邀请我们 我……我没穿上盛宴着装
GANDALF: Kind of you to invite us, I'm... not really dressed for diner.

1097
01:27:34,079 --> 01:27:35,779
你从来就没穿上过
ELROND: Well, you never are.

1098
01:27:56,164 --> 01:27:58,383
这是兽咬剑
ELROND: This is Orcrist...

1099
01:27:58,735 --> 01:28:00,330
斩妖精剑
the Goblin- cleaver.

1100
01:28:00,693 --> 01:28:05,206
闻名的刀刃……由西方高等精灵锻造
A famous blade, forged by the High Elves of the West.

1101
01:28:06,127 --> 01:28:07,601
我的国王
My kin.

1102
01:28:08,491 --> 01:28:10,209
愿它能为你好好效力
May it serve you well.

1103
01:28:10,428 --> 01:28:13,373
这是格兰瑞
And this is Glamdring...

1104
01:28:14,280 --> 01:28:18,215
敌击剑，贡多林国王之剑
The Foe- hammer, sword of the king of Gondolin.

1105
01:28:18,356 --> 01:28:21,156
这些剑是为第一纪元妖精战争铸造
These swords were made for the Goblin wars of the First-

1106
01:28:21,174 --> 01:28:22,357
我不在乎，伙计
BALIN: I wouldn't bother, laddie.

1107
01:28:22,529 --> 01:28:25,995
剑因在战争中的伟大功绩而得名
Swords are named for the great deeds they do in war.

1108
01:28:26,089 --> 01:28:28,889
你是说我的剑没经历过战争？
What're you saying, my sword hasn't seen battles?

1109
01:28:29,056 --> 01:28:31,210
我还不确定它是把剑
I'm not actually sure it is a sword.

1110
01:28:32,342 --> 01:28:34,339
更像是开信刀，真的
More of a letter opener, really.

1111
01:28:35,496 --> 01:28:37,001
你怎么拿到这些的？
ELROND: How did you come with these?

1112
01:28:37,096 --> 01:28:40,447
我们在东方大道的巨怪储物窖里找到的
GANDALF: We found them in a troll hoard on the Great East road,

1113
01:28:40,945 --> 01:28:43,380
而后就遇到半兽人伏击了
shortly before we were ambushed by orcs.

1114
01:28:44,264 --> 01:28:48,386
你们在东方大道上做什么呢？
And what were you doing on the Great East road?

1115
01:28:50,066 --> 01:28:52,227
我们的事与精灵无关
THORIN: Our business is no concern of Elves.

1116
01:28:52,270 --> 01:28:55,143
拜托，索林，给他看地图
GANDALF: For goodness sake. Thorin, show him the map!

1117
01:28:55,228 --> 01:28:57,328
那是我的子民的遗产
THORIN: It is the legacy of my people.

1118
01:28:57,514 --> 01:28:59,334
我的职责是保护它！
It's mine to protect!

1119
01:28:59,749 --> 01:29:01,207
包括我们的秘密
As are its secrets.

1120
01:29:01,317 --> 01:29:03,879
别再让我为矮人的固执烦恼了
GANDALF: Save me from the stubbornness of dwarves.

1121
01:29:04,143 --> 01:29:06,718
你的高傲会让你垮台
Your pride will be your downfall.

1122
01:29:07,322 --> 01:29:11,522
你面前站着一个中土世界 为数不多的能看懂那地图的人
You stand here in the presence of one of the few in Middle-earth who can read that map.

1123
01:29:11,719 --> 01:29:13,820
让艾隆大人看看！
Show it to Lord Elrond!

1124
01:29:21,320 --> 01:29:21,920
索林，别给

1125
01:29:32,346 --> 01:29:33,765
伊鲁柏
ELROND: Erebor.

1126
01:29:35,281 --> 01:29:38,528
你对这地图有什么兴趣？
What is your interest in this map?

1127
01:29:40,060 --> 01:29:41,880
主要是学术上的
GANDALF: It's mainly academic.

1128
01:29:42,283 --> 01:29:46,163
如你所知，这些东西有时包含隐藏讯息
As you know, this sort of artifacts sometimes contains hidden texts.

1129
01:29:52,521 --> 01:29:55,471
你还看得懂古矮人语，对吧？
You still read ancient dwarvish, do you not?

1130
01:30:00,178 --> 01:30:02,707
对，色斯文伊西尔
ELROND: Yeah, “Cirth ithil”.

1131
01:30:03,438 --> 01:30:05,087
月亮如尼文
GANDALF: Moon runes...

1132
01:30:06,047 --> 01:30:07,663
当然
Of course.

1133
01:30:08,651 --> 01:30:10,391
一个容易被忽视的东西
An easy thing to miss.

1134
01:30:10,704 --> 01:30:14,342
在此，对，要读懂月亮如尼文必须借助
ELROND: And in this case, that is true. Moon runes can only be read by the light

1135
01:30:14,353 --> 01:30:19,633
与它们被写下那天相同季节的 相同形状的月亮的月光
of the moon of the same shape and season as the day on which they were written.

1136
01:30:20,155 --> 01:30:21,600
你能读懂它们？
THORIN: Can you read them?

1137
01:30:26,627 --> 01:30:29,773
这些如尼文写于近乎两百年前的
ELROND: These runes were written on a mid-summer's eve

1138
01:30:29,795 --> 01:30:34,339
某个仲夏节前夜，当时是新月
by the light of a crescent moon nearly two hundred years ago.

1139
01:30:34,754 --> 01:30:37,876
似乎你注定该来瑞文戴尔
It would seem you were meant to come to Rivendell.

1140
01:30:38,533 --> 01:30:40,616
命运与你同在，索林・橡木盾
Fate is with you, Thorin Oakenshield.

1141
01:30:40,687 --> 01:30:43,914
今晚相同的月亮照耀着我们
The same moon shines upon us tonight.

1142
01:31:03,268 --> 01:31:07,875
当鸫敲石时站在灰石旁
“Stand by the grey stone when the thrush knocks,”

1143
01:31:08,056 --> 01:31:12,858
都林日落日最后的余晖
“and the setting sun with the last light of Durin's Day

1144
01:31:12,875 --> 01:31:16,388
将照耀在钥匙孔上
will shine upon the key- hole”.

1145
01:31:16,497 --> 01:31:17,557
都林日？
BILBO: Durin's Day?

1146
01:31:17,588 --> 01:31:19,682
那是矮人的新年
GANDALF: It the dwarves' new year,

1147
01:31:19,690 --> 01:31:24,184
那时秋季最后一次月落和冬季 第一次日出将同时出现于空中
when the last moon of Autumn and the first sun of Winter appear in the sky together.

1148
01:31:24,311 --> 01:31:25,632
这是坏消息
THORIN: This is ill news.

1149
01:31:26,262 --> 01:31:29,166
夏季要结束了，都林日立马就来了
Summer is passing. Durin's Day will soon be upon us.

1150
01:31:29,229 --> 01:31:30,349
我们还有时间
BALIN: We still have time.

1151
01:31:30,507 --> 01:31:31,389
时间，做什么？
BILBO: Time, for what?

1152
01:31:31,445 --> 01:31:32,616
找到入口
BALIN: To find the entrance.

1153
01:31:33,117 --> 01:31:36,897
我们必须找到绝对准确的位置和时机
We have to be standing at exactly the right spot, at exactly the right time.

1154
01:31:37,021 --> 01:31:40,776
那时，只有那时，门才会开启
Then, and only then... can the door be opened.

1155
01:31:40,847 --> 01:31:44,651
那么这就是你们的目的，进入大山
ELROND: So this is your purpose. To enter the mountain.

1156
01:31:45,556 --> 01:31:46,956
那又怎么了？
THORIN: What of it?

1157
01:31:47,030 --> 01:31:50,608
有些人认为这不明智
ELROND: There are some who would not deem it wise.

1158
01:31:51,608 --> 01:31:53,428
你指的是谁？
GANDALF: Who do you mean?

1159
01:31:54,120 --> 01:31:58,406
你不是唯一看护中土世界的卫士
You are not the only guardian to stand watching over Middle- earth.

1160
01:32:23,306 --> 01:32:26,406
那些矮人……主人

1161
01:32:28,606 --> 01:32:30,406
我们跟丢了

1162
01:32:34,206 --> 01:32:37,606
被臭精灵伏击，我们……

1163
01:32:38,206 --> 01:32:40,706
我不要借口

1164
01:32:47,306 --> 01:32:51,006
我要矮人国王的头

1165
01:32:52,206 --> 01:32:53,706
我们人数不足

1166
01:32:53,906 --> 01:32:55,406
我们无能为力

1167
01:32:56,306 --> 01:32:59,706
我差点丢了命

1168
01:33:00,406 --> 01:33:01,706
你最好……

1169
01:33:03,706 --> 01:33:05,106
为此偿命

1170
01:33:25,406 --> 01:33:30,706
矮人渣很快会露面

1171
01:33:32,606 --> 01:33:33,706
放出口令

1172
01:33:35,406 --> 01:33:37,406
砍了他们的头有赏

1173
01:34:00,835 --> 01:34:01,955
庞柏！
Bombur!

1174
01:34:05,309 --> 01:34:07,614
[Everyone laughing]

1175
01:34:08,705 --> 01:34:12,868
不论我们有没帮忙，这些矮人都会往山里前进
GANDALF: With or without our help, these dwarves will march on the mountain.

1176
01:34:13,053 --> 01:34:15,949
他们决意收回自己的家园
They're determined to reclaim their homeland.

1177
01:34:16,114 --> 01:34:21,025
我不相信索林・橡木盾 觉得自己该对任何人负责
I do not believe Thorin Oakenshield feels that he's answerable to anyone.

1178
01:34:21,456 --> 01:34:26,702
我也不要，因为他们不是要向我负责
ELROND: Nor for that matter am I, cause it's not me they must answer to.

1179
01:34:38,397 --> 01:34:40,199
盖拉德利尔夫人
Lady Galadriel.

1180
01:34:41,146 --> 01:34:42,943
米斯兰达
Mithrandir.

1181
01:34:44,443 --> 01:34:46,743
好久不见了

1182
01:34:49,343 --> 01:34:51,843
岁月或许改变了我

1183
01:34:53,343 --> 01:34:55,943
但罗瑞安夫人却没变

1184
01:35:01,787 --> 01:35:05,511
我不知道艾隆大人请您来了
GANDALF: 'd no idea Lord Elrond had sent for you.

1185
01:35:05,606 --> 01:35:07,006
他没有
SARUMAN: He didn't.

1186
01:35:07,668 --> 01:35:09,001
是我
I did.

1187
01:35:17,584 --> 01:35:18,984
萨鲁曼
Saruman.

1188
01:35:19,396 --> 01:35:22,925
你近来很忙，老朋友
You've been busy of late, my friend.

1189
01:35:24,277 --> 01:35:26,097
告诉我，甘道夫……
Tell me, Gandalf...

1190
01:35:26,626 --> 01:35:32,147
你以为你这些计划和安排会无人察觉吗？
Did you think these plans and schemes of yours would go unnoticed?

1191
01:35:32,288 --> 01:35:33,688
无人察觉？
GANDALF: Unnoticed?

1192
01:35:35,164 --> 01:35:36,564
不，我……
No, I...

1193
01:35:36,688 --> 01:35:39,455
我只是在做自己觉得对的事
I'm simply doing what I feel to be right.

1194
01:35:39,474 --> 01:35:43,033
恶龙……一直困扰着你
Galadriel: The dragon... has long been on your mind.

1195
01:35:43,425 --> 01:35:45,245
对，夫人
GANDALF: It is true, my Lady.

1196
01:35:45,426 --> 01:35:47,650
斯矛戈不对任何人效忠
Smaug owes allegiance to no one.

1197
01:35:48,096 --> 01:35:50,196
但如果他与敌人一道
But if he should side with the enemy,

1198
01:35:51,016 --> 01:35:53,816
他们会利用恶龙制造可怕后果
the dragon could be used to terrible effect.

1199
01:35:54,216 --> 01:35:55,616
什么敌人？
SARUMAN: What enemy?

1200
01:35:56,342 --> 01:35:58,855
甘道夫，敌人被打败了
Gandalf, the enemy is defeated.

1201
01:35:59,355 --> 01:36:01,175
索伦被击败了
Sauron is vanquished.

1202
01:36:01,512 --> 01:36:03,612
他再也无法恢复全力
He can never regain his full strength.

1203
01:36:04,385 --> 01:36:05,697
甘道夫……
Gandalf...

1204
01:36:05,798 --> 01:36:09,803
四百年来，我们都和平地生活
for four hundred years, we have lived in peace,

1205
01:36:09,827 --> 01:36:12,832
这是艰难获得，小心提防来的和平
a hard won watchful peace!

1206
01:36:12,903 --> 01:36:14,926
我们……我们和平吗？
GANDALF: Are we- are we at peace?

1207
01:36:17,025 --> 01:36:19,260
巨怪从山里下来
Trolls have come down from the mountains,

1208
01:36:19,315 --> 01:36:21,875
他们袭击村落，毁坏农田
they are raiding villages, destroying farms.

1209
01:36:22,125 --> 01:36:24,302
半兽人在路上攻击我们
Orcs have attacked us on the road.

1210
01:36:24,451 --> 01:36:26,411
这不是战争的序曲
ELROND: Hardly a prelude to war.

1211
01:36:26,521 --> 01:36:28,487
你总是爱插手
SARUMAN: Always you must meddle.

1212
01:36:29,027 --> 01:36:31,024
寻找不存在的麻烦
Looking for trouble where none exist!

1213
01:36:31,212 --> 01:36:32,612
让他说
GALADRIEL: Let him speak.

1214
01:36:34,358 --> 01:36:39,202
除了邪恶的斯矛戈之外，还有个东西
GANDALF: There is something at work beyond the evil of Smaug,

1215
01:36:39,472 --> 01:36:41,572
一个更为强大的东西
something far more powerful.

1216
01:36:43,057 --> 01:36:48,166
我们可以对它熟视无睹 但它不会忽视我们，我向你们保证
We can remain blind to it, but it will not be ignoring us, that I can promise you.

1217
01:36:48,500 --> 01:36:50,920
在绿林里满是病态
A sickness hides over the Greenwood.

1218
01:36:51,388 --> 01:36:56,338
那里的樵夫现在叫它 幽暗密林，他们……他们说……
The woodsmen who live there now call it Mirkwook, and uh, they s-  they say...

1219
01:36:58,033 --> 01:37:03,458
别停下，告诉我们樵夫说了什么
SARUMAN: Well, don't stop now, tell us what the woodsmen say?

1220
01:37:03,575 --> 01:37:06,973
他们说有个死灵法师住在多尔哥多
GANDALF: They speak of a Necromancer, living in Dol Guldur,

1221
01:37:06,988 --> 01:37:10,212
那是能唤起死灵的巫师
a sorcerer who would summon the dead.

1222
01:37:10,464 --> 01:37:11,782
荒唐
SARUMAN: That's absurd.

1223
01:37:12,150 --> 01:37:14,694
世界上没有这种力量
No such power exists in this world.

1224
01:37:14,851 --> 01:37:19,374
这个……死灵法师不过是个凡人
This... Necromancer is nothing more than a mortal man.

1225
01:37:19,645 --> 01:37:22,228
涉猎黑暗魔法的巫师
A conjurer dabbling in black magic.

1226
01:37:22,362 --> 01:37:24,674
我也这么想，但是
GANDALF: And so I though too. But...

1227
01:37:25,165 --> 01:37:26,290
瑞达加斯特看见了
Radagast has seen- .

1228
01:37:26,291 --> 01:37:27,405
瑞达加斯特？
Radagast has seen- C Radagast?

1229
01:37:27,866 --> 01:37:30,666
别跟我提褐袍巫师瑞达加斯特
Do not speak to me of Radagast the Brown.

1230
01:37:31,318 --> 01:37:33,138
他是个蠢货
He's a foolish fellow.

1231
01:37:33,339 --> 01:37:37,393
他很奇怪，我承认，他过着隐居生活
Well... he's odd, I grant you, he lives a solitary life.

1232
01:37:37,665 --> 01:37:38,727
不是那样
SARUMAN: It's not that.

1233
01:37:38,829 --> 01:37:42,123
是他吃了过多蘑菇
It's his excessive consumption of mushrooms.

1234
01:37:42,616 --> 01:37:46,504
那些弄乱了他的脑子，弄黄了他的牙齿
They've addled his brain, and yellowed his teeth.

1235
01:37:47,004 --> 01:37:48,404
我警告过他
I warned him.

1236
01:37:48,752 --> 01:37:51,960
一个埃斯塔力在丛林里游荡不合适 （埃斯塔力：人类口中的巫师）
It is unbefitting one of the Istari wandering the wood...

1237
01:37:51,992 --> 01:37:54,038
你带了东西来
GALADRIEL (V.O.): You carry something.

1238
01:37:55,976 --> 01:37:58,435
是瑞达加斯特给你的
It came to you from Radagast...

1239
01:37:59,083 --> 01:38:01,385
他在多尔哥多找到的
He found it in Dul Guldur...

1240
01:38:02,721 --> 01:38:03,841
对
GANDALF: Yes.

1241
01:38:05,469 --> 01:38:06,869
给我看
GALADRIEL: Show me.

1242
01:38:09,904 --> 01:38:13,044
[Saruman keeps on speaking]

1243
